<subSubSection id="6DC56513FFECFFE0E2C2A4B2CD737315" pageId="2" pageNumber="303" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="25603698FFECFFE0E2C2A4B2CD737315" blockId="2.[151,1437,1604,1919]" pageId="2" pageNumber="303">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFECFFE0E2C2A4B2CF027284" bold="true" box="[199,322,1748,1774]" pageId="2" pageNumber="303">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
May be distinguished from other species of the genus by a combination of the following character states: sides of 
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFECFFE0E341A49FCF207378" box="[324,352,1785,1810]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="303">im</emphasis>
(MA, MP) parallel and converging basally at steeper angle [
<taxonomicName id="E2DF4D1BFFECFFE0E615A49FCAD97379" authorityName="Makarkin &amp; Archibald" authorityYear="2013" box="[1040,1177,1785,1811]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Archaeochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="303" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="profracta">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFECFFE0E615A49FCAD97379" box="[1040,1177,1785,1811]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="303">A. profracta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="E2DF4D1BFFECFFE0E6A2A49FCB637378" authorityName="Archibald &amp; Makarkin" authorityYear="2015" box="[1191,1315,1784,1811]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Archaeochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="303" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sanikwa">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFECFFE0E6A2A49FCB637378" box="[1191,1315,1784,1811]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="303">A. sanikwa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="E2DF4D1BFFECFFE0E737A49FCBD57379" baseAuthorityName="Cockerell" baseAuthorityYear="1914" box="[1330,1429,1785,1811]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Archaeochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="303" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fracta">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFECFFE0E737A49FCBD57379" box="[1330,1429,1785,1811]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="303">A. fracta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
: sides of 
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFECFFE0E2FEA57BCF57735C" box="[251,279,1821,1846]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="303">im</emphasis>
converging basally at low angle]; 2m-cu located distinctly proximad middle of 
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFECFFE0E6BCA57BCA95735C" box="[1209,1237,1821,1846]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="303">im</emphasis>
[
<taxonomicName id="E2DF4D1BFFECFFE0E6EDA57BCB33735D" authorityName="Makarkin &amp; Archibald" authorityYear="2013" box="[1256,1395,1821,1847]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Archaeochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="303" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="profracta">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFECFFE0E6EDA57BCB33735D" box="[1256,1395,1821,1847]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="303">A. profracta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="E2DF4D1BFFECFFE0E781A57BCEB37330" authorityName="Archibald &amp; Makarkin" authorityYear="2015" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Archaeochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="303" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sanikwa">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFECFFE0E781A57BCEB37330" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="303">A. sanikwa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
: slightly distad or slightly proximad middle of 
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFECFFE0E102A527CD637330" box="[775,803,1857,1882]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="303">im</emphasis>
]; costal margin not convex in middle of costal space [
<taxonomicName id="E2DF4D1BFFECFFE0E781A527CE9A7315" baseAuthorityName="Cockerell" baseAuthorityYear="1914" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Archaeochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="303" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fracta">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFECFFE0E781A527CE9A7315" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="303">A. fracta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="E2DF4D1BFFECFFE0E2EDA503CF347314" authority="Makarkin &amp; Antell &amp; Archibald, 2022" authorityName="Makarkin &amp; Antell &amp; Archibald" authorityYear="2022" box="[232,372,1892,1919]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysopidae" genus="Archaeochrysa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neuroptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="303" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cockerelli" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFECFFE0E2EDA503CEB97315" box="[232,249,1893,1919]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="303">A</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFECFFE0E302A502CF347314" box="[263,372,1892,1918]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="303">cockerelli</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="0C9857F1FFECFFE0E379A503CF977314" box="[380,471,1893,1919]" pageId="2" pageNumber="303" rank="species">
<emphasis id="17ABEA8AFFECFFE0E379A503CF907315" bold="true" box="[380,464,1893,1919]" pageId="2" pageNumber="303">sp. nov</emphasis>
.
</taxonomicNameLabel>
: convex through costal space].
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
